'''铜绿微囊藻'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Microcystis aeruginosa''）是一種出現在淡水中的[[藍菌|藍菌]]，會產生[[有害藻華|有害藻華]]，具有一定的生態學與經濟重要性<ref name="Encyclopedia of Life: Chroococcales">{{cite web|title=Chroococcales|url=http://www.eol.org/pages/3238|publisher=EOL|accessdate=24 June 2011|archive-date=2010-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229220552/http://www.eol.org/pages/3238|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Oberholster>{{cite web|last=Oberholster|first=PJ|title=Microcystis aeruginosa: souce of toxic microcystins in drinking water|url=http://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:VBcNNhpjT88J:https://tspace.library.utoronto.ca/bitstream/1807/3750/1/jb04029.pdf+microcystis+aeruginosa&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESgfDSjCPS4BqnJvY1z2c0HFx7ZQ7B6ccBXl0Bq-jrsdk7n6__RyGhk9pWru6lt_Kisp1zNlsOiH_ef4t2osE7p__aFB9F-xwQb5ffbimxhl3wVR96eeSP_2Jqz29rPR62lLmZTp&sig=AHIEtbSZk24-gDPAOyrBgmCLORm_dkSw5w|work=Microcystis aeruginosa: souce of toxic microcystins in drinking water|publisher=African Journal of Biotechnology March 2004 Volume 3 pp 159-168|accessdate=24 June 2011|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609225755/http://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3AVBcNNhpjT88J%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Ftspace.library.utoronto.ca%2Fbitstream%2F1807%2F3750%2F1%2Fjb04029.pdf+microcystis+aeruginosa&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESgfDSjCPS4BqnJvY1z2c0HFx7ZQ7B6ccBXl0Bq-jrsdk7n6__RyGhk9pWru6lt_Kisp1zNlsOiH_ef4t2osE7p__aFB9F-xwQb5ffbimxhl3wVR96eeSP_2Jqz29rPR62lLmZTp&sig=AHIEtbSZk24-gDPAOyrBgmCLORm_dkSw5w|dead-url=no}}</ref>。铜绿微囊藻是在[[優養化|優養化]]的淡水中最常見的有毒藍菌藻華來源<ref name=Oberholster/>。

==特徵==
如同其學名顯示的，[[微囊藻屬|微囊藻屬]]的特徵為小型的細胞，細胞大小僅有3至8微米<ref name="udn">{{cite web |url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/campus/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=406821 |author=[[鄚朝陽|鄚朝陽]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819040538/http://mag.udn.com/mag/campus/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=406821 |title=水庫水質解析／恐怖微囊藻毒 喝了恐罹肝炎 |publisher=聯合報 |date=2012-08-13 |accessdate=2016-07-21 |archivedate=2012-08-19 |language=zh-hant |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，且其外沒有鞘包覆<ref>{{cite web|title=Cyanobacteria: Microcystis|url=http://silicasecchidisk.conncoll.edu/LucidKeys/Carolina_Key/html/Microcystis_Main.html|work=The Silica Secchi Disk|publisher=Connecticut College: The SilicaSecchi Disk|accessdate=24 June 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080326200658/http://silicasecchidisk.conncoll.edu/LucidKeys/Carolina_Key/html/Microcystis_Main.html|archivedate=2008-03-26}}</ref>。細胞常聚集成肉眼可見的群落，這些群落本為圓形，經過時間發展可能會產生孔洞並呈不規則形狀。[[原生質體|原生質體]]的顏色是淺藍綠色，但因細胞中具有充滿空氣的[[囊泡|囊泡]]在光下可能呈暗色，這是[[光學顯微鏡|光學顯微鏡]]下微囊藻的鑑別特徵之一。囊泡提供微囊藻足夠的浮力，使其停留在有足夠光線和[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]提供生長的水層。

==生態==
铜绿微囊藻較偏好高溫，但毒性與最高生長率不一定有關聯，在實驗室培養中，攝氏32度具有最高的生長率，但毒性最強的溫度是攝氏20度。溫度低於攝氏15度時其生長會被顯著的抑制。除了毒素外，微囊藻形成藻華時淡水溶氧量的顯著降低也會導致水中動物的死亡<ref>{{cite journal|last=Padmavathi|first=P|coauthors=K. Veeraiah|title=Studies on the influence of M. aeruginosa on the ecology and fish production of carp culture ponds|journal=African Journal of Biotechnology|date=6/04/2009|volume=8|issue=9|pages=1911–1918|url=http://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:OwOnahthwzwJ:www.ajol.info/index.php/ajb/article/view/60424/48662+microcystis+aeruginosa+fish+oxygen&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESiG-9ZxvSXRfWgCy_Z5pOEpA_yhlInUq2lXrbqP-z-katP-coKMTtkNx8dM5YReydCX3PCnal9vuQ7sBGSY4SI8A-JhSV8O45a4J5CfCqPg5kNg2mH-VFQFloWfuxmEYSSou29z&sig=AHIEtbTBoCow_KNi18hpPYnCUB2bZ-c2gw|accessdate=24 June 2011|archive-date=2016-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528082609/http://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3AOwOnahthwzwJ%3Awww.ajol.info%2Findex.php%2Fajb%2Farticle%2Fview%2F60424%2F48662+microcystis+aeruginosa+fish+oxygen&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESiG-9ZxvSXRfWgCy_Z5pOEpA_yhlInUq2lXrbqP-z-katP-coKMTtkNx8dM5YReydCX3PCnal9vuQ7sBGSY4SI8A-JhSV8O45a4J5CfCqPg5kNg2mH-VFQFloWfuxmEYSSou29z&sig=AHIEtbTBoCow_KNi18hpPYnCUB2bZ-c2gw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一種水生被子植物[[聚藻|聚藻]]可以產生[[鞣花酸|鞣花酸]]、[[沒食子酸|沒食子酸]]、[[連苯三酚|連苯三酚]]和[[兒茶素|兒茶素]]，這些[[聚酚|聚酚]]化合物可產生[[化感作用|化感作用]]，對铜绿微囊藻的生長產生抑制<ref name=Nakai>Myriophyllum spicatum-released allelopathic polyphenols inhibiting growth of blue-greenalgaeMicrocystis aeruginosa. Satoshi Nakai, Yutaka Inoue, Masaaki Hosomi and Akihiko Murakami, Water Research, Volume 34, Issue 11, 1 August 2000, Pages 3026–3032, {{doi|10.1016/S0043-1354(00)00039-7}}</ref>。

==毒素==
[[Image:Microcystin-LR.svg|thumb]]]]
铜绿微囊藻可以產生[[神經毒素|神經毒素]][[脂多糖|脂多糖]]<ref name="LPS toxicity Microcystis">{{cite journal|last=Mayer|first=Alejandro M. S.|coauthors=Jonathan A. Clifford|title=Cyanobacterial Microcystis aeruginosa Lipopolysaccharide Elicits Release of Superoxide Anion, Thromboxane B2, Cytokines, Chemokines, and Matrix Metalloproteinase-9 by Rat Microglia|journal=[[Toxicological_Sciences|Toxicological Sciences]]|date=2|year=2011|volume=121|issue=1|url=http://toxsci.oxfordjournals.org/content/121/1/63.short?rss=1|accessdate=25 June 2011|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701185707/https://academic.oup.com/toxsci/article/121/1/63/1640584|dead-url=no}}</ref>與{{link-en|肝毒素|hepatotoxins}}{{link-en|微囊藻素|microcystins}}。微囊藻素是一些環狀{{link-en|非核糖体多肽|Nonribosomal peptide}}的合稱，由{{link-en|脱氢丙氨酸| dehydroalanine}}衍生物和{{link-en|ADDA氨基酸|ADDA (amino acid)}}等[[非蛋白胺基酸|非蛋白胺基酸]]組成，可強烈抑制第一型與第二型蛋白質[[磷酸酶|磷酸酶]]，對動植物都有毒性，對[[肝臟|肝臟]]的毒性很強，也和{{link-en|全脂炎|Pansteatitis}}有關<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pwrc.usgs.gov/health/rattner/rattner_blackwaternwr.cfm|title=Harmful Algal Blooms and Bird Die-offs in Chesapeake Bay:  A Potential Link?|author=Barnett A. Rattner, Glenn H. Olsen, Peter C. McGowan, Betty K. Ackerson, and Moira A. McKernan|publisher=USGS-Patuxent Wildlife Research Center and Fish and Wildlife Service, Chesapeake Bay Field Office|accessdate=2013-03-31|archive-date=2013-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130305091408/http://www.pwrc.usgs.gov/health/Rattner/rattner_blackwaternwr.cfm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==經濟重要性==
由於在理想的環境下铜绿微囊藻可以持續產生對肝有害的微囊藻素，其為[[水質|飲用水汙染]]的來源之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Cyanobacterial Toxins: Microcystin-LR in drinking water|url=http://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:hB3G0xgpX3wJ:www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/dwq/chemicals/cyanobactoxins.pdf+microcystis+aeruginosa+drinking+water&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEEShcbKCATULdoWmYMmdDDfKwkvn9AGxBiBjfD74GLQKBu2-IxU8u1OVVbVugaxxqc6DQqe50Pmj7xLim9GPFB9i6LHxN5KjoBimSZXBLAIJ3buRhH9nGmCkHiF3O0xOWqsk2qLiY&sig=AHIEtbSVIloCd3Jyb6SYRqRn-8oLPhlUNg|work=Background document for development of WHO Guidelines for Drinking Water Quality|publisher=World Health Organization (WHO)|accessdate=24 June 2011|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417090256/http://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3AhB3G0xgpX3wJ%3Awww.who.int%2Fwater_sanitation_health%2Fdwq%2Fchemicals%2Fcyanobactoxins.pdf+microcystis+aeruginosa+drinking+water&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEEShcbKCATULdoWmYMmdDDfKwkvn9AGxBiBjfD74GLQKBu2-IxU8u1OVVbVugaxxqc6DQqe50Pmj7xLim9GPFB9i6LHxN5KjoBimSZXBLAIJ3buRhH9nGmCkHiF3O0xOWqsk2qLiY&sig=AHIEtbSVIloCd3Jyb6SYRqRn-8oLPhlUNg|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且這種毒素對熱的抗性高，甚至以[[活性碳|活性碳]]吸附、加入[[氯|氯]]或[[臭氧|臭氧]]消毒也無法完全消除<ref name="udn"></ref>。對經濟的影響包括為了減輕毒素需要在淨水上花費的額外成本，和發生有害藻華的河湖需暫時封閉對當地旅遊業造成傷害<ref name="Effects on tourism and local water quality">{{cite web|last=Somek|first=Hasim|title=A Case Report: Algal Bloom of Microcystis aeruginosa in a Drinking-Water Body, Eğirdir Lake, Turkey|url=http://www.trjfas.org/pdf/issue_8_1/177_179.pdf|work=A Case Report: Algal Bloom of Microcystis aeruginosa in a Drinking-Water Body, Eğirdir Lake, Turkey|publisher=Turkish Journal of Fisheries and Aquatic Sciences|accessdate=27 June 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004044736/http://www.trjfas.org/pdf/issue_8_1/177_179.pdf|archivedate=2011-10-04}}</ref>。

也有研究顯示铜绿微囊藻可以產生[[2,6-二叔丁基對甲酚|2,6-二叔丁基對甲酚]]，這種物質主要在[[食品添加劑|食品添加劑]]中被用作為[[抗氧化劑|抗氧化劑]]，在工業上也具有許多用途<ref name="BHTalgae">{{cite journal |author=Babu B, Wu JT |title=Production of Natural Butylated Hydroxytoluene as an Antioxidant by Freshwater Phytoplankton |journal=Journal of Phycology |volume=44 |issue=6 |pages=1447–1454 |url=http://ntur.lib.ntu.edu.tw/bitstream/246246/162863/1/22.pdf |doi=10.1111/j.1529-8817.2008.00596.x |date=December 2008 |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2014-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404115128/http://ntur.lib.ntu.edu.tw/bitstream/246246/162863/1/22.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

